         <abstract>
            <p>A series expansion is given for the computation of the integral over (-∞, ∞) of the nth power of the Voigt function for use in spectral line calculations with Doppler broadening. A nine significant figure table is presented for n up to 25 and for a wide range of values of the second parameter on a microfiche card in this issue.</p>
          </abstract>
